description: Step into one of the most hilarious and heartwarming scenes from Zoom: Academy for Superheroes, where kids from across the country show up to audition for the ultimate honor—becoming the next generation of superheroes! 💥From invisibility mishaps to super strength that’s just a bit too strong, this tryout session is anything but ordinary. Led by the reluctant hero Captain Zoom, the team searches for young recruits who might save the world—or at least survive training camp! 😄Watch as each kid reveals their quirky and sometimes unpredictable powers. Some impress, some cause a few laughs (and minor explosions), but all of them have something special. It's a chaotic mix of chaos, comedy, and surprising moments of heart. ❤️Whether you're here for the action, the laughs, or the nostalgia of early 2000s superhero films, this scene is a must-watch. Shark Tank Nepal is the first-ever Nepali edition of the globally acclaimed business reality show.
The 20-episode season will showcase Nepal's most promising entrepreneurs pitching their business ideas to a panel of successful business leaders ("Sharks") for potential investment and mentorship. 

बिश्वप्रसिद्ध बिजनेस रियालिटी टीभी शो शार्क ट्यांकको नेपालका संस्करण शार्क ट्यांक नेपाल सुरु भइसकेको छ ।
